bago ka pa handa.

236
00:17:04,607 --> 00:17:06,810
Sorry...

237
00:17:09,384 --> 00:17:12,374
na wala akong sinabi sayo.

238
00:17:14,454 --> 00:17:17,034
Hindi lang ako sigurado...

239
00:17:19,523 --> 00:17:21,851
Hindi ako sigurado...

240
00:17:23,801 --> 00:17:27,523
kung malalaman mo ang totoo sa lalong madaling panahon...

241
00:17:30,408 --> 00:17:33,734
magpapalala ng iyong kalagayan.

242
00:17:37,901 --> 00:17:39,840
Ayos lang, Mom.

243
00:17:41,546 --> 00:17:44,026
Alam kong mabuti ang ibig mong sabihin.

244
00:17:45,329 --> 00:17:48,628
Minahal at pinag-aalala mo ako.

245
00:17:52,282 --> 00:17:58,028
Feeling ko... medyo walang laman kahit papaano.

246
00:18:03,432 --> 00:18:07,939
Solar, pangako.

247
00:18:09,319 --> 00:18:11,799
Kapag handa ka na,

248
00:18:13,017 --> 00:18:16,630
Ako na ang magsasabi sa iyo ng lahat.

249
00:18:17,903 --> 00:18:19,931
Ngunit sa ngayon,

250
00:18:20,949 --> 00:18:24,023
