382
00:30:03,724 --> 00:30:06,928
Isa siyang TV show host.

383
00:30:10,253 --> 00:30:13,319
Ngunit pagkatapos niyang ipanganak si Sun,

384
00:30:14,514 --> 00:30:17,824
