392
00:30:49,932 --> 00:30:51,849
Ako si Solar.

393
00:30:51,849 --> 00:30:54,140
Ang ibig sabihin ng solar ay maliwanag na sikat ng araw,

394
00:30:54,140 --> 00:30:57,764
